<section xml:id="sec-decimal-numbers" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Meaning From Bits: Decimal Numbers</title>

  <p>Interpreting binary bits as numbers can take multiple forms. 
    The oldest and most leveraged number format is the integer.</p>


